Package: suitestrings
Title: A consistent approach to common string operations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("David", "Foord", , "david.foord@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Convenient wrappers around base R string manipulation functions, for cleaning, combining and transforming strings, operating on regular expression and reorganising character vectors.
